title: Final HOPR Token Launch Voting
body:
As explained in our [HOPR Genesis DAO announcement blog](https://link.medium.com/f1EOOYhIJdb), we will now move to the final stage of the HOPR Token Launch. 

Here are the 3 most popular valid proposals for the mechanism governing the HOPR token launch. For more information on modifications and disqualified proposals, see [this forum post](https://forum.hoprnet.org/t/hopr-token-launch-voting-phase/271). 

All DAO participants are now invited to vote for their preferred proposal.

All three proposals contain the following phases and conditions:
- Phase 1: A presale consisting of a simple smart contract on xDAI, whitelisted only to DAO participants
- presale token price is fixed at $0.05
- presale token allocation is capped (individual purchase cap) at the number of presale tokens divided by the number of Genesis DAO participants (around 3000)
- if the presale has not raised $500k after 24h, the individual purchase cap will be raised by 50% every 3h until $500k is collected
- any tokens not sold in the presale will roll over to the LBP in Phase 2.
- Phase 2: Balancer LBP running for 72h, with maximal weights of 98:2 guaranteeing a starting price of at least $0.3, final weight is 40:60
- Phase 3: All liquidity from Balancer LBP is withdrawn and moved into a Uniswap pool, liquidity mining incentives are added for 3 months


**Proposal 1**
Distribution: 20m (presale) / 59m (LBP) / 6m (Uni mining)
Based on
https://snapshot.page/#/genesis-dao.hopr.eth/proposal/QmV9Bdc5h1Bfnr4r5Cx6fr1QJ1uwA98C82oPxowbA8zELX

**Proposal 2**
Distribution: 55m (presale) / 25m (LBP) / 5m (Uni mining)
50% of presale tokens are liquid after conclusion of the LBP phase, the other 50% become liquid after 18 months
Based on
https://snapshot.page/#/genesis-dao.hopr.eth/proposal/QmeFxXryZFwhQxW5trvneR7hBXmMRoAiYn5HWwsBh4GJis

**Proposal 3**
Distribution: 50m (presale) / 30m (LBP) / 5m (Uni mining)
